---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | PosturePro"
  description="PosturePro privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: February 1, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-lg">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        When you make a purchase, we collect:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
        <li>Name and contact information</li>
        <li>Shipping and billing address</li>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>Payment information (processed securely by Snipcart/Stripe)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
        <li>Process and fulfill your orders</li>
        <li>Send shipping updates and order confirmations</li>
        <li>Provide customer support</li>
        <li>Send marketing emails (only if you opt in)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We use industry-standard encryption and security measures to protect your
        personal information. Payment processing is handled by Snipcart and Stripe,
        which are PCI-DSS compliant.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We use cookies to improve your shopping experience and for analytics.
        You can disable cookies in your browser settings.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We use the following third-party services:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
        <li>Snipcart (shopping cart and checkout)</li>
        <li>Stripe (payment processing)</li>
        <li>Google Analytics (website analytics)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        You have the right to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
        <li>Request a copy of your data</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        Questions about our privacy practices? Contact us at
        <a href="mailto:privacy@posturepro.com" class="text-green-600 hover:underline">privacy@posturepro.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <a href="/" class="inline-block mt-8 text-green-600 hover:underline">‚Üê Back to Shop</a>
  </div>
</Layout>
